Summary: Orange teardrop shape glowing & traveling in the sky.
divs: Sighting DetailsAt first we thought it was a firework down Naples Bay. It rose straight up but then instead of exploding, it began to move towards us. Then it veered westward over the Golf of Mexico. Soon #2 appeared - then #3. #4 & #5 appeared within moments of each other & together took the same path. We are still watching for more.
